    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
