    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then chop your <strong>green beans</strong> into bite-size pieces</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
