      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and<strong> garam masala</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> diced chicken</strong> <strong>breast</strong> and <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until browned all over</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
