          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> with the <strong>ground almonds</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> with your <strong>sultanas</strong> and <strong>chopped green beans </strong>and cook for 7-8 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
