      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's cooked, stir through your<strong> double cream</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a very generous crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>creamy chicken mughlai curry</strong></p>",
